"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640540968,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"bkLdvtNf5q88rR6BxQEer_0WLNjnhPeV55DB2xPnCaQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xA68b585583495A59EF2aDE2ad568302aa72cb224\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"uA3P_G0gImy063GyL01900OcolxVLxgCFdH6JBpCrA8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2qI2QlOAKXD6Op-FlEazc4qtyobZZCwIDAaD7RaS4UM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"7RphZHXqHAdbppDTI7FX9RF-24dZ4oNH2Np-lrhU9K_koJ3MbhtADJFwYpb6utmoudL20Se1eQPNl6DeYJHCnQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4dd46d4ad289668df3ea2709c3f79613192af17bc4c6e831735746eb57ea7d6429926bb7c8c281cb0870859d8c9669ad938ca7e68fde66501b97a60a73b5e4b71b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"uA3P_G0gImy063GyL01900OcolxVLxgCFdH6JBpCrA8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2qI2QlOAKXD6Op-FlEazc4qtyobZZCwIDAaD7RaS4UM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi